code: @Override protected Lockable.LockableTypeSerializer<E> createOuterSerializerWithNestedSerializers(TypeSerializer<?>[] nestedSerializers) {     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     TypeSerializer<E> elementSerializer = (TypeSerializer<E>) nestedSerializers[0].     return new Lockable.LockableTypeSerializer<>(elementSerializer). }
@Override protected TypeSerializer<?>[] getNestedSerializers(Lockable.LockableTypeSerializer<E> outerSerializer) {     return new TypeSerializer<?>[] { outerSerializer.getElementSerializer() }. }
